@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_tepkst(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (wp.abs((v0 + 0.94 + v0 + 0.65)) * wp.exp((v1 + 0.30 - v2 + 0.35)))
    tmp = (((v0 + 0.97 * v0 + 0.03) + v0) - ((v1 + 0.72 * v0 + 0.45) - wp.abs(v2 + 0.20)))
    tmp = tmp
    v2 = (v1 / (wp.cos(v0 + 0.70) * wp.abs(tmp + 0.01)))
    v0 = (wp.abs(wp.exp(v2 + 0.51)) * (0.55 / 0.29))
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.exp(wp.exp(v0 + 0.96)))
    v2 = tmp
    v2 = (v2 / v2)
    data[tid] = v0
